<template>
      <input class=" input__checkbox--icon" type="checkbox" v-model="listCheckboxSellected" :value="checkboxValue">
</template>
<script>
export default {
    props:{checkboxValue, listChecked},
    watch:{
        listCheckboxSellected:function(newValue){
            this.$emit("update:listChecked", newValue);
        }
    },
    data() {
        return {
            listCheckboxSellected:[]
        }
    },
}
</script>
<style scoped>

</style>
